message: Hi Bob, I'm selling this product for $9000. It's in excellent condition and worth every penny.  Let me know if you're interested!
Hi Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I think we can work something out closer to my budget. Would you consider $8500 for the product?
Bob, I appreciate your counteroffer.  I'm willing to come down to $8750.  This is a fair price considering the value of the product.  Let me know what you think!
Hello Alice, thank you for adjusting your offer. I appreciate it. However, I still believe we could reach an agreement closer to my budget. Would $8600 be acceptable for the product?
